<Class name="CM_Hire" id="f9e15d19-dd40-4593-8d0e-f2fea92e4050">
    <superclass name="CM_TITransaction"/>
    <persistentAllowed/>
    <sharedTransientAllowed/>
    <subclassPersistentAllowed/>
    <subclassSharedTransientAllowed/>
    <subclassTransientAllowed/>
    <transientAllowed/>
    <text>

These transactions can only be created manually in the UiCommonSchema::CMUI_TITransMaint form, 
which is accessible from the Cargo Transaction List form CMUI_TransactionEnquiry.

Creating this transaction does not set the hireDT on the TI. hireDT is use for future storage only.</text>
    <DbClassMap file="transact"/>
